<PageMeta category="Adoption" variant="brand" updated="Updated 2026-05-14" />

      <h1>Smart Data Challenge 2025</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Sponsored by the <strong>Department for Business and Trade (DBT)</strong>, run
        through the Smart Data Challenge Programme (SDCP). The Moverly + OPDA entry won
        the <strong>SDCP Innovators prize</strong> in December 2025 for the
        <em>Digital Property Pack</em> use case. A companion <em>Digital Identity</em>
        entry was also submitted.
      </p>

      <div class="callout callout--key">
        <div class="callout__label">Public announcement</div>
        <p>
          OPDA's <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CO1uLzQTiSc" target="_blank" rel="noopener">"Winners of the Smart Data Challenge 2025!"</a> video
          (5:38) summarises the outcome. The original Moverly prize-pitch is on
          Vimeo: <a href="https://vimeo.com/1140770692" target="_blank" rel="noopener">vimeo.com/1140770692</a>,
          with transcript at
          <a class="resource-link" href="/resource.html?path=source/05-engagement/videos-youtube/embedded/vimeo_1140770692.txt"><code>source/05-engagement/videos-youtube/embedded/vimeo_1140770692.txt</code></a>.
        </p>
      </div>

